{"article_id":"g6pqgSqpTA94YOr2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrat Jon Ossoff finished behind Republican Karen Handel in Georgia ' s special House election on Tuesday night ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"but the real loser could turn out to be House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"While Pelosi is in no immediate danger","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"of losing her House perch ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"she ' s increasingly becoming the face of a period of Democratic stagnation","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that ' s seen a once-mighty majority systematically deteriorate during her tenure .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"you ' d have to be an idiot","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"to think","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"we could win the House with Pelosi at the top , \"","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Rep. Filemon Vela , D-Tex. , bluntly told Politico .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"\" Nancy Pelosi is not the only reason","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that Ossoff lost ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"but she certainly is one of the reasons . \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"As Speaker of the House in 2009 , Pelosi presided over a 255-seat majority","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"which was wiped out by the next election ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"when Democrats fell to 193 seats .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"In three election cycles since then , Pelosi ' s party has netted a single House seat .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Those","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"seeking to be part of the next Democratic majority","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"are already seeking separation from Pelosi .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Democrat Joe Cunningham ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"running to unseat Republican Mark Sanford in South Carolina ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"tweeted","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"soon after announcing his candidacy :","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"\" If elected ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"I will not vote for Nancy Pelosi for speaker .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Time to move forward","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"and win again . \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Rep. Kathleen Rice , D-N.Y. , told CNN","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"\" we need a leadership change .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"It ' s time for Nancy Pelosi to go , and the entire leadership team . \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Rep. Tim Ryan , D-Oh. ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"who ran against Pelosi in the last leadership election ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"didn ' t invoke his former rival by name ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"but did by association ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"the Democratic product has grown spoiled and rotten in recent years .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"\" Here is the truth :","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"the Democratic Party has a toxic brand , one","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that is worse than Donald Trump ' s in many parts of the country , \"","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Ryan wrote in a Medium post .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Pelosi is in an undeniably tough spot .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Her longevity and leadership position makes her tough to unseat ;","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"however , it also makes her a target for the more progressive wing of her party","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"that is upset with those in so-called \" establishment \" posts .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"And her unpopularity with Republicans of conservative and moderate stripes has made her an easy anchor","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to tie Democratic candidates to in competitive races .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"\" I certainly hope","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"the Democrats do not force Nancy P out .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"That would be very bad for the Republican Party","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"- and please let Cryin ' Chuck stay ! \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"President Trump tweeted on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"also referencing Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The schadenfreude among GOP leaders was n't limited to Trump 's Twitter feed , either .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"\" I hope","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"they keep Nancy for 10 more years .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"At least another decade , \"","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"former House Speaker Newt Gingrich told \" Fox & Friends \" on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"\" We have all the ads done .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"They worked perfectly in Georgia .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"We know how to run against a Nancy Pelosi-run party . \"","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"A source close to Pelosi told Fox News","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"the criticism `` bothers her , ''","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"particularly as it 's coming from all angles ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"as opposed to any attacks","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"she faced after the November elections .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"\" But this is different , \"","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"said one source .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"\" Death by a thousand cuts . \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"One senior House Democratic member told Fox News :","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"\" There ' s going to be discontent ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"but it ' s more pronounced now .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"There is some angst about the elections . \"","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Pelosi ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"first elected in 1987 from her California district ,","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"has sought to stop the landslide beneath her feet","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"by emphasizing the positive takeaways from the highly competitive Georgia race ,","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"which Democrats poured money and time into in hopes","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"of dealing President Trump a high-profile defeat .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"In a \" Dear Colleague \" letter","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"obtained by The New York Times ,","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"Pelosi ,","depth":6},{"id":83,"text":"who has resisted all calls","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"to step aside ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"spoke of a unifying message","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"\" we can all embrace and utilize in our districts. \"","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"During a recent caucus meeting , Pelosi also said","depth":5},{"id":88,"text":"the shooting of House Majority Whip Steve Scalise by a disgruntled Democratic voter may have contributed to the Georgia loss ,","depth":5},{"id":89,"text":"Politico reported .","depth":4},{"id":90,"text":"But the spin","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"being deployed by Pelosi and others in leadership","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"is growing tougher to digest for some in the House .","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"\" It was probably one of the more disturbing caucus meetings","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that I ' ve ever been in , \"","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Rice told Politico .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"\" And everyone pretty much sat in silence ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"and I ' d like to think","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"that they were as shocked","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"as I was","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that they were hearing the spin","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that was being put on this loss . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":175,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":119,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":103,"right":118,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":114,"right":117,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":106,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":104,"right":105,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":104,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},